citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 3:30 pm on
04/09/2015. Inspector knocked and rang the doorbell several times. Attempted to make contact with licensee by
cell phone and left message. Departed the facility at 4:05 pm and left business card on the door.
